---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout 
  title="About Yilong | 30+ Years Medical Scrubs Manufacturer" 
  description="Anhui Yilong Environmental Protection Technology Co., Ltd. - 30+ years of medical scrubs manufacturing. OEKO-TEX certified, SGS verified factory. OEM/ODM for global healthcare brands."
  keywords="medical scrubs manufacturer, OEM scrub factory, hospital uniform supplier, China scrub manufacturer, private label scrubs"
>
  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="relative bg-slate-900 text-white py-20 md:py-28 overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-10">
      <div class="absolute inset-0" style="background-image: url('data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg width=60 height=60 viewBox=%220 0 60 60%22 xmlns=%22http://www.w3.org/2000/svg%22%3E%3Cg fill=%22none%22 fill-rule=%22evenodd%22%3E%3Cg fill=%22%239C92AC%22 fill-opacity=%220.4%22%3E%3Cpath d=%22M36 34v-4h-2v4h-4v2h4v4h2v-4h4v-2h-4zm0-30V0h-2v4h-4v2h4v4h2V6h4V4h-4zM6 34v-4H4v4H0v2h4v4h2v-4h4v-2H6zM6 4V0H4v4H0v2h4v4h2V6h4V4H6z%22/%3E%3C/g%3E%3C/g%3E%3C/svg%3E');"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 text-center relative z-10">
      <div class="inline-block px-4 py-1 bg-secondary/20 border border-secondary/30 rounded-full text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-secondary mb-6">Factory Since 1994 · Anhui, China</div>
      <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-black mb-6 leading-tight">About <span class="text-secondary">Yilong</span> Scrubs</h1>
      <p class="text-slate-300 text-base md:text-lg max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">30 years of precision manufacturing. One specialty: medical scrubs. Serving 60+ countries with OEKO-TEX® certified fabrics and SGS verified factory quality.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Stats Bar -->
  <section class="bg-slate-900 border-t border-slate-800">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-0 divide-x divide-slate-800">
        <div class="py-8 md:py-10 text-center px-4">
          <div class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-black text-secondary mb-1">30+</div>
          <p class="text-[10px] md:text-xs text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-widest">Years Manufacturing</p>
        </div>
        <div class="py-8 md:py-10 text-center px-4">
          <div class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-black text-secondary mb-1">60+</div>
          <p class="text-[10px] md:text-xs text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-widest">Countries Served</p>
        </div>
        <div class="py-8 md:py-10 text-center px-4">
          <div class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-black text-secondary mb-1">100%</div>
          <p class="text-[10px] md:text-xs text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-widest">Factory QC Inspect</p>
        </div>
        <div class="py-8 md:py-10 text-center px-4">
          <div class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-black text-secondary mb-1">10 Sets</div>
          <p class="text-[10px] md:text-xs text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-widest">Low MOQ · Ships Worldwide</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Company Story -->
  <section class="py-16 md:py-24 bg-white">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        <div class="inline-block px-3 py-1 bg-slate-100 text-slate-600 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest rounded-full mb-6">Our Story</div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-4xl font-black mb-8 text-slate-900">We Only Make Scrubs.<br/>That's the Point.</h2>
        <div class="space-y-5 text-slate-600 leading-relaxed text-base md:text-lg">
          <p><strong class="text-slate-900">Anhui Yilong Environmental Protection Technology Co., Ltd.</strong> was founded in 1994 in Anhui Province, China. For over three decades, we have focused exclusively on the research, development, and manufacturing of medical scrubs and healthcare apparel.</p>
          <p>Unlike garment factories that diversify across many product categories, Yilong has never made anything but medical scrubs. This single focus has allowed us to refine our fabric formulas, optimize our production processes, and build deep expertise in what healthcare professionals actually need from their uniforms.</p>
          <p>Today, we serve brands, hospitals, and distributors across 60+ countries — from North America and Europe to Southeast Asia, the Middle East, and Africa. Every piece that leaves our factory has passed 100% quality inspection before shipment.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Why Choose Us -->
  <section class="py-16 md:py-24 bg-slate-50">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="text-center mb-12 md:mb-16">
        <div class="inline-block px-3 py-1 bg-slate-200 text-slate-600 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest rounded-full mb-4">Why Yilong</div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-4xl font-black text-slate-900">Why 60+ Countries Choose Yilong</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6 md:gap-8">
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 border border-slate-100 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition">
          <div class="text-3xl mb-4">🏭</div>
          <h3 class="font-black text-lg mb-3 text-slate-900">Focus = Expertise</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">30 years of scrubs-only manufacturing. We don't make workwear, uniforms, or anything else — our entire R&D budget goes into one product category.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 border border-slate-100 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition">
          <div class="text-3xl mb-4">🧪</div>
          <h3 class="font-black text-lg mb-3 text-slate-900">Proprietary Fabric Formulas</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">Three fabric tiers (205 GSM / 180 GSM / 130 GSM) developed in-house. We can adjust composition ratios to match your target market requirements.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 border border-slate-100 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition">
          <div class="text-3xl mb-4">📦</div>
          <h3 class="font-black text-lg mb-3 text-slate-900">Small Brand Friendly MOQ</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">Color MOQ from 10 sets/color. Logo customization from 20 sets/style. We actively support startups building their first private label collection.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 border border-slate-100 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition">
          <div class="text-3xl mb-4">🎨</div>
          <h3 class="font-black text-lg mb-3 text-slate-900">7 Logo工艺 Types</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">Embroidery, screen printing, heat transfer, DTG, foil stamping, pad printing, and sublimation — one-stop-shop for all your branding needs.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 border border-slate-100 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition">
          <div class="text-3xl mb-4">⏱️</div>
          <h3 class="font-black text-lg mb-3 text-slate-900">Guaranteed Lead Times</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">Samples in 7 days. Production in 15–30 days. We keep records of on-time delivery performance — no excuses, no surprises.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 border border-slate-100 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition">
          <div class="text-3xl mb-4">🌍</div>
          <h3 class="font-black text-lg mb-3 text-slate-900">DDP Shipping Worldwide</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">Sea freight, air freight, and express. DDP service (taxes & customs cleared included) available for USA, Canada, Mexico, LATAM, and the Middle East.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Certifications -->
  <section class="py-16 md:py-24 bg-white border-t border-slate-100">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <div class="inline-block px-3 py-1 bg-green-100 text-green-700 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest rounded-full mb-4">Certifications</div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-4xl font-black text-slate-900 mb-4">Quality You Can Verify</h2>
        <p class="text-slate-500 max-w-xl mx-auto">All our claims are backed by internationally recognized certifications and third-party lab testing.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <div class="text-center p-8 bg-slate-50 rounded-2xl border border-slate-200">
          <div class="text-5xl mb-4">✓</div>
          <h3 class="font-black text-lg text-slate-900 mb-2">OEKO-TEX® Standard 100</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm">Every fabric batch tested for harmful substances. Safe for prolonged skin contact. International textile safety standard.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="text-center p-8 bg-slate-50 rounded-2xl border border-slate-200">
          <div class="text-5xl mb-4">✓</div>
          <h3 class="font-black text-lg text-slate-900 mb-2">SGS Factory Verification</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm">On-site verified manufacturing facility. Third-party audited production capacity, quality systems, and labor standards.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="text-center p-8 bg-slate-50 rounded-2xl border border-slate-200">
          <div class="text-5xl mb-4">✓</div>
          <h3 class="font-black text-lg text-slate-900 mb-2">ISO Quality Management</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm">ISO-certified quality management system. 100% QC inspection before shipment. Full traceability from fabric to finished garment.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Markets Served -->
  <section class="py-16 md:py-24 bg-slate-900 text-white">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 text-center">
      <div class="inline-block px-3 py-1 bg-secondary/20 border border-secondary/30 text-secondary text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest rounded-full mb-6">Global Reach</div>
      <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-4xl font-black mb-4">Serving 60+ Countries Across 6 Continents</h2>
      <p class="text-slate-400 max-w-xl mx-auto mb-12">From brand-new startups in Brooklyn to established hospital groups in Dubai, Yilong delivers quality scrubs worldwide.</p>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-4 text-sm md:text-base">
        <span class="px-5 py-2 bg-slate-800 rounded-full text-slate-300">🇺🇸 North America</span>
        <span class="px-5 py-2 bg-slate-800 rounded-full text-slate-300">🇪🇺 Europe</span>
        <span class="px-5 py-2 bg-slate-800 rounded-full text-slate-300">🇸🇦 Middle East</span>
        <span class="px-5 py-2 bg-slate-800 rounded-full text-slate-300">🌏 Southeast Asia</span>
        <span class="px-5 py-2 bg-slate-800 rounded-full text-slate-300">🌍 Africa</span>
        <span class="px-5 py-2 bg-slate-800 rounded-full text-slate-300">🌎 Latin America</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="py-16 md:py-20 bg-secondary text-white text-center">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-4xl font-black mb-4">Ready to Work with a True Manufacturer?</h2>
      <p class="text-emerald-100 max-w-xl mx-auto mb-8">No agents. No middlemen. Factory direct. Get your sample quote in 24 hours.</p>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
        <a href="/contact" class="bg-white text-secondary px-8 py-4 rounded-full font-bold hover:bg-slate-100 transition shadow-lg">Get a Free Sample Quote</a>
        <a href="/products" class="bg-transparent border-2 border-white text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-full font-bold hover:bg-white/10 transition">View Product Catalog</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
